I"D<p>This is a community curated list of different ways to use Open Peer Power. Most of these examples are using the <a href="/getting-started/automation/">automation</a> integration and other built-in <a href="/integrations/#automation">automation related</a> and <a href="/integrations/#organization">organization</a> integrations available.</p>
<p>For <a href="/integrations/python_script/"><code>python_script:</code> examples</a> visit the <a href="https://community.openpeerpower.io/c/projects/scripts">Scripts section</a> in our forum.</p>
<p>New recipes can be added via the <a href="https://github.com/OpenPeerPower/openpeerpower.io/tree/current/_cookbook">openpeerpower.io repository</a>.</p>
